{"tid":1708602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自製被罷工","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:14:50.000Z","uid":17046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5137597594dd7caacb93a1948be39712252da315","tid":1708602,"uid":17046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"大家成日話罷唔到工<br />\n今朝大家就一嘗被罷工既滋味<br />\n成效我覺得都work架喎<br />\n<br />\n如果聽日大家又想被罷工<br />\n唔洗下下靠勇武手足既<br />\n不妨早d著套返工衫出黎一齊塞<br />\n又可以掩護手足<br />\n成功左又唔洗返工<br />\n諗到都爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以大家今晚早d訓 要早d出門口先返到工架</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xpmEJUx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxpmEJUx.jpg&h=e976a411&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9jOCey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9jOCey.jpg&h=ec2d1584&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85cb1470667bc6759a707f3786db6ffe986d7a43","tid":1708602,"uid":17046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"我要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早d出門口先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949f3d7d1210535355813dc2356a0fa619070a4e","tid":1708602,"uid":17046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"我要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早d出門口先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b48542dee7d2a5a15bc7097305d8a57c004b96","tid":1708602,"uid":17046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"我要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早d出門口先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5a3394b5cc8ce86da5af996fa7d8f3b523fda5","tid":1708602,"uid":17046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco